          "username": "pdragosh"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-03-21 12:42:34.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nGood idea Jorge - I like that. Put it in policy/model. And yes stack traces are not useful to the end user. Either I can do this in my spare cycles today or maybe Liam??",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "a88fd52f70665ccbc67821e1b4acde42c6726d7a",
